snippet.textDisplay:
Sooooooooooooooooo....

Ya Know Yall Gonna Need To Make An Angel Version of this Special Valentines Pin Right?? RIGHT!?

CAUSE....Back Of His Head.....Im Just Saiyan!! Heart....Right THERE....Big As Day!!!!

Hashtag: Missed Opportunity....

Aaaaaaand Then Yall Gonna Need To Make A Moxxie And Millie Half Heart Version That Makes Them Be Snuggled Up When Ya Put The Two Together.....

Aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaand Then Ya Gotta Make Their Plushies So Couples Can Buy A Moxxie Plush with a Millie Pin and a Millie Plush with a Moxxie Pin THEN Exchange Them With Their Beloveds.

This Will Become The New Way To Say I Love You. And It Will Be Good. Cause Ya Know....THEY A COUPLE.....And Valentines Day Is About COUPLES And Love....And Mushy Ass Shit....GAG.

Hashtag: Another Missed Opportunity....

Aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaand then, I suppose you could also make a Stolas and Blitzo Paired Pin Set thats a play on the Moxxie and Millie one....Just for the shits and giggles of it.

But mostly I think making a Paired broken Heart Moxxie and Millie pin set that turns into one heart when put together would be cool and fit alot better with the Valentines Love theme since....Ya Know....Alastor is Asexual and all....I mean hes Awesome and the BEST and all that....Buuuut....Its kinda like a little....Wasted on him.....Cause Hes Alone....ATM....Canonically....I think still? IDK....Im always late to things so he might already be married to Angel....Or Charlie....Or Vaggie....MWAHAHAHAHAHAHA!!!!

Either way, In my fanfic world him and Angel are an adorable couple with some awkwardly cute sexual tensions brought on by Angels brand of....Proclivities and Alastors old timey mannerisms which I find to be Brilliantly Adorable and my favorite part of the entire cast cause I like that kind thing personally. Hense loner status cause People like Alastor dont actually exist anymore....Le Sigh.

Soooooooooooooooo Anyway, Yeah...I got their Pins and plushies on Lock already and even got their plushies and all their pins for my Bestie cause I love her to Hell and back again. Hahahaha!! So I look forward to getting my Heart Shaped Ali pin whenever it manages to make it here.
